    "summary": "I am a writer and documentary maker dedicated to writing and filming about Africa, specifically about travel, culture and Africa's relations with the west. I have published 8 books about Africa and 2 children's books and have directed a number of feature TV documentaries about Africa. At the moment I am making a series of short documentaries about African traditional healers. You can watch them on my Youtube channel youtube.com/spiritsofafrica which has had more than 150.000 views.  I am writing a new book for my publisher Balans/De Bezige Bij about 16th century discoverer Jan Huygen van Linschoten. I am also developing Karma Credits, a new internet tool that combines a social network with a game (not a video game) and creates online communities with strong personal interaction. For Karma Credits, I am looking for a development partner.\nHave a look at my websites www.tonvanderlee.nl and www.spiritsofafrica.com to find out more!",
